msgid "welcome_message"
msgstr    "✨ <b>Welcome!</b> ✨\n\n
"📩 <b>Send messages or media</b> (📷 photos, 🎥 videos, or 🎞️ GIFs), and the bot will forward them for you without revealing your identity.\n\n"
"🔄 The original forwarding name will be <b>removed</b> and replaced with the bot’s name, ensuring complete anonymity.\n\n"
"🔒 <b>Your privacy is our priority!</b>\n\n"
"⚠️ <i>Note:</i>\n"
"❌ Buttons and captions will be <b>automatically removed</b>.\n\n"
"👉 <b>👉 Try it now! Send your media and see how it works</b>"


